      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Cut your <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into small bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>potatoes</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiling water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 12-15 min or until fork-tender</p><p>Once cooked, drain, and return to the pot</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
